node.accessibility_caption: Photo by JJ_MOBILEPHOTOGRAPHY in The Women's Building of San Francisco with @sur_la_terre. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:

@monkeymuesli
.
be sure to visit our featured artist’s gallery and show them some ig l💜ve.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by JJ_MOBILEPHOTOGRAPHY in Hirtshals with @miakbh. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
Hello again the jj_mp family 👋 It is James (@jhyattphoto) here. How is/has your Wednesday going/gone?
.
When I saw this photo in the #jj_mobilephotography tag it really took my breath away. Mia's capture is absolutely gorgeous. I love the soft tones and beautiful light. The scene is wonderful (who does not love the beach?) The pair of people walking along are perfectly framed by the grass in the foreground, which wonderfully breaks up the image into triangles. Superb photo Mia! 😍
.
Congratulations @miakbh and thank you for tagging and following 🙏
.
Please visit our featured artist’s gallery and show them some IG ❤!

node.text:
Hey the jj_mp community 👋 It is James (@jhyattphoto) here. I hope you are all well 👍
.
This photo really caught my eye in the #jj_mobilephotography tag earlier. Maarten's stunning photo is full of compositional delights, which all pull your eyes towards the wonderfully silhouetted people. For starters there are the leading lines of the ground and wall. Then the framing using the ever decreasing repeating triangles. It all adds up to one
Beautifully captured photo Maarten! 😍 Ps. Just look at that gorgeous light too!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by JJ_MOBILEPHOTOGRAPHY on August 30, 2021 tagging @rosemarygamburg. May be an image of nature and body of water.

node.text:
Marika highlights this serene beauty as her 5th and final selection from the weekend. Huge thanks to you, Marika, for the wonderful theme, selections, and being such a joy to work with! Hey, jj mobile fam! Please help us thank Marika for such an awesome job. We invite you to also check out her gallery and show her some jj mp appreciation! Here are her thoughts on the selection and challenge:
.

“Rosemary’s green forest and pure lake with the fallen tree leading the eye to floating clouds is calming my soul ☁️ Hope you can feel it too! Congratulations Rosemary 💚”. 

Huge thanks to you all absolutely talented and lovely people who wanted to take part this weekend’s JJMP Challenge “Reflections of nature” 🤍 It was so hard for me to choose from all those wonderful pictures ❤️ Thank you for giving so much this weekend ❤️ And thanks again Dee for this opportunity, I enjoyed every moment! Happy Autumn to ya all ❤️ - @marikahv 

Tag: #jj_mp_rosemarygamburg

node.text:

I hope you’re in for a double-dose of fun and natural beauty today, because thanks to Marika’s @marikahv “Reflections of Nature” weekend challenge, the amazing photos y’all tagged, and Marika’s excellent selections, that’s what we have in store for you here at JJMP all day long!!! 😍💕
.
.
After much admiring and reflecting through the tag gallery, Marika was able to narrow down her choices to 5 fabulous faves. 
So without further ado, let’s find out what she has to say about her first of five favorites in no particular order:

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by JJ_MOBILEPHOTOGRAPHY in The Netherlands with @saskiaqua. May be an image of horse and nature.

node.text:
Hello everyone! It’s Dee again to share my final feature of the night with you!😊🙋🏻‍♀️
•
•
This shot by Saskia @saskiaqua demanded  my attention right away! 🤩 
The dynamic contrast of the wildness of the horse and even the sky above to the soft tones and beauty of the lavender flowers below are a striking combo!
Saskia also managed to capture a successful and rare combo of an action and nature shot all in one.👌💜 🐎  A happy accident indeed, Saskia!😃👍
.
.
To see more of Saskia’s wild and beautiful photos, please visit her gallery @saskiaqua and spread lots of JJMP love while you’re there too!😘💜
.
I look forward to seeing you next week!😘❤️🙋🏻‍♀️ Dee (@iheart_alfresco_photos) 
.
.
Featured: @saskiaqua 
Tag: #jj_mp_saskiaqua

Device: Samsung Galaxy
